divs: Sighting DetailsLEAVING COFFE SHOP AT 6:50 AM. HAPPENED TO LOOK UP INTO THE WESTERN SKY AND SAW THIS BRIGHT SILVER OBJECT. AT FIRST I THOUGHT IT WEAS A PLANE BUT THEN IT STOPPED AND HOVERED FOR ABOUT 30 SECONDS. I TOOK 3 PICTURES OF IT WITH MY CELLPHONE.
